  <description>
    <p>ImageFan Reloaded is a light-weight tab-based image viewer, supporting multi-core processing.</p>
	<p>ImageFan Reloaded features mouse-only interaction, using the left and the right mouse buttons, and the mouse wheel:</p>
	<ul>
	  <li>the left mouse button for selecting tabs, folders and images, and for opening, zooming in and out, and dragging images</li>
	  <li>the right mouse button for returning from the opened image to the main view</li>
	  <li>the mouse wheel for scrolling through folders and thumbnails, and for navigating back and forward through opened images</li>
	</ul>
  </description>
  
